00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
and replace the 50 with what you want your initial velocity to be.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:08.000
So if you wanted your initial velocity to be 60 m/s, then you replace the 50 with a 60.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.000
You don't need to include the units.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:15.000
And if you wanted the launch angle to be 20°, then you need to replace this 10 with 20.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
Again, you don't need to write the word degrees or anything like that.

